    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single chip, scratch, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is pristine and spotless, still carrying that new-car scent with leather seats that show no wear and electronics that function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like a brand-new model, requiring zero investment or repairs.",
