    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? This car has been so good to me and still runs like a total dream. It\u2019s been well-loved and carefully maintained, making it the perfect choice if you want something dependable and stylish without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got a super smooth drive and plenty of life left in it\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
