    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing a visceral connection to the rear-mounted M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, ensuring the structural and mechanical longevity of the chassis. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the precise turn-in and lateral stability these cars are known for. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight tolerances, offering a pure driving experience for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
