    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and pride of ownership. Finished in a classic deep metallic, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, showing only the minor road-wear consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery has been treated regularly to maintain its supple feel, and all electronic features\u2014from the climate control to the infotainment system\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with recent fluid changes and a fresh set of tires ensuring it\u2019s ready for the road immediately. Whether you\u2019re commuting or taking a weekend getaway, this car offers a smooth, quiet, and dependable ride. It is a well-loved, honest example that is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
